Package: drpm
Type: Package
Title: Dependent Random Partition Model
Version: 0.1.2
Authors@R: person(given = "Garritt", family = "L. Page", email = "page@stat.byu.edu", role = c("aut", "cre", "cph"))
Maintainer: Garritt L. Page <page@stat.byu.edu>
Description: Provides an R-wrapper function that access C-code that fits models that employ a 
              dependent random partition model as detailed in Page et al. <arXiv:1912.11542>.
              All the models detailed in the paper are available as special cases. In addition,
              it is possible to include an ``initial'' partition as detailed in 
              <arXiv:1912.11542>.
License: GPL
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: true
